      "fontSize": 28.75287783900619,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Root Memory Chunk is initialized during library initiation\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Root Memory Chunk is initialized during library initiation\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 360,
      "versionNonce": 721155539,
      "index": "ad",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "uTXx2av_Wqldbb0_J6V8g",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 3420.964724409853,
      "y": 515.0995027331163,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 1824.4643810242162,
      "height": 51.91491832042783,
      "seed": 1756436055,
      "groupIds": [
        "JdnDI6uTPOeVwVSdZb9N2"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1713005274467,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 41.531934656342266,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Global Linked List is used for maintaining the location of the root memory chunk and size",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Global Linked List is used for maintaining the location of the root memory chunk and size",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 887,
      "versionNonce": 189088989,
      "index": "ae",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "SJsHtf_aStrRYZtToboux",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 646.5782432961153,
      "y": 36.74061249488864,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 791.4755907746643,
      "height": 359.41097298757734,
      "seed": 1597633975,
      "groupIds": [
        "JdnDI6uTPOeVwVSdZb9N2"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "uegfiM544gXxIazCZperA",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1713005274467,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 28.752877839006185,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Goal: To Reduce the number of mallocs\n\nThis is achieved through process based memory\nchunks.\n\nIf the process memory chunks size limit has been\nexceeded, a new process memory chunk double the size\nof the previous one is swapped out in it's place. In this\ncase, the previous process memory chunk is freed\nin the top memory chunk",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Goal: To Reduce the number of mallocs\n\nThis is achieved through process based memory\nchunks.\n\nIf the process memory chunks size limit has been\nexceeded, a new process memory chunk double the size\nof the previous one is swapped out in it's place. In this\ncase, the previous process memory chunk is freed\nin the top memory chunk",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 614,
      "versionNonce": 709084019,
      "index": "af",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "P0WQnfkDIS-MKjo4EEgOF",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 390.33153107349176,
      "y": 2086.809392543872,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 814.9759448946018,
      "height": 179.70548649378867,
      "seed": 354116311,
      "groupIds": [
        "JdnDI6uTPOeVwVSdZb9N2"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1713005274467,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 28.752877839006185,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Since each process has to have a memory chunk, \nwithout the top memory chunk, each memory chunk needs\n to malloc from the os. To avoid this, a top memory\nchunk is maintained from which the children memory chunks \ncan get the required memory ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Since each process has to have a memory chunk, \nwithout the top memory chunk, each memory chunk needs\n to malloc from the os. To avoid this, a top memory\nchunk is maintained from which the children memory chunks \ncan get the required memory ",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
