      "fontSize": 28.752877839006185,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "When the memory limit of the root memory chunk itself is exceeded, new root memory chunk is created with double the size\nof the old one and new memory chunks are stored in the new root chunk. Once the usages of the old root are done,\nit is dropped",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When the memory limit of the root memory chunk itself is exceeded, new root memory chunk is created with double the size\nof the old one and new memory chunks are stored in the new root chunk. Once the usages of the old root are done,\nit is dropped",
